author: Bhaskar Live
title: 7.4-magnitude quake hits Indonesia - Bhaskar Live English News
description: Jakarta, Dec 30 | A 7.4-magnitude earthquake struck the southern coast of Indonesia’s Maluku province on Thursday morning, the country’s Meteorological, Climatological and Geophysical Agency said. No casualties or damage have been reported so far, reports Xinhua news agency. The quake struck at 1.25...
